ğŸ§  WHAT SHOULD YOU THINK/DO WHEN YOU SEE THAT?
Think: "If itâ€™s homegrown and runs stuffâ€¦ Iâ€™m opening it up."

âœ… Your CPTS Brain Should Say:
"Whatâ€™s in this .exe?"

